high_descs: Turn left and walk around the island to the coffee maker.
Open the cupboard above the coffee maker and grab the mug.
turn to the left and in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the mug on the plate, warm the mug, and then remove the mug.
Turn right and stand in front of the microwave.
Place the mug under the spout of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn left, go to the bar, then turn right and go straight.
Take the mug from the cabinet above the counter.
Turn left, to go toward the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Turn right toward the counter with the coffee maker.
Place the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to the left and then the right to find the coffee maker.
Open the top cabinet and get the mug out, shut the door.
Take the mug and turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the mug inside. Turn it on, then get the mug out and shut the door again.
Take the mug and turn slightly right.
Place the mug under the coffee maker.
